\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Robotic Process Automation (RPA) utilizes software robots to automate repetitive and rule-based tasks, freeing up human workers to focus on more complex and strategic activities. RPA is widely used in industries such as finance, healthcare, and customer service to improve efficiency, accuracy, and compliance. Key features of RPA include the ability to mimic human actions, integrate with existing systems, and scale operations quickly. By automating tasks such as data entry, invoice processing, and customer support, RPA helps organizations reduce costs, enhance productivity, and achieve higher levels of customer satisfaction.}